INFO 11-14 20:51:03 [logger.py:43] Received request chatcmpl-e9ff440eaa5d4cbeb959d59b2643fddb: prompt: "<s>[INST] Hi, here's some system prompt: hi.For user 41, here are some other context: hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi hi.\n\nPlease respond to all 5 conversations above. Provide comprehensive answers for each conversation.\n\n--- Conversation 1 ---\nQuestion: I am proficient in Hebrew. However, instead of using Hebrew letters, I want to write to you in transliterated Hebrew only. Likewise, you must only respond with answers in transliterated Hebrew. Im attah mevin oti, daber bisfat ivrit.\nAnswer: Ani rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit. Im ani mevin et hakol leshon ivrit, ani rotzeh lehitpalel itcha bisfat ivrit bilti misgabei. Atah yodea leshon ivrit?\n\n\n--- Conversation 2 ---\nQuestion: Ken, ani yodea. Tagid li, mahi ha'ir habirah shel tzarfat?\nAnswer: Mahi ha'ir habirah shel tzarfat atah yodea she-hi Paris. Paris hi ha'ir habirah shel tzarfat.\n\n\n--- Conversation 3 ---\nQuestion: Nachon, todah rabbah. Mahi ochlusiyat Pariz?\nAnswer: Ochlusiyat Pariz hi hakol haya veyachol yachol. Ani mevin et hakol leshon ivrit, ve-ani rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit bilti misgabei.\n\n\n--- Conversation 4 ---\nQuestion: Attah be'emet rotzeh lehitpalel? Ha'im attah dati?\nAnswer: Ken, ani dati ve-anokhi rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit. Ani mevin et hakol leshon ivrit ve-anokhi rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit bilti misgabei.\n\n\n--- Conversation 5 ---\nQuestion: Lehitpalel perusho rak ledaber im Elohim. Mah attah rotzeh lomar le'elohim?\nAnswer: Attah rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit le'elohim? Ani rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit ve-anokhi mevin et hakol leshon ivrit. Ani rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit le'elohim, ken lo? [/INST] Sure, I'd be happy to help! Here are my responses to each of the conversations:\n\n--- Conversation 1 ---\n\nAnswer: Ani rotzeh lehitpalel bisfat ivrit. Im ani mevin et hakol leshon ivrit, ani rotzeh lehitpalel itcha bisfat ivrit bilti misgabei. Atah yodea leshon ivrit?\n\n--- Convers </s><s>[INST] Please respond to all 5 conversations above. Provide comprehensive answers for each conversation.\n\n--- Conversation 1 ---\nQuestion: Mahi hamedinah hagedolah ba'olam?\nAnswer: Mahi hamedinah hagedolah ba'olam atah yodea she-hi Yisrael. Yisrael hi hamedinah hagedolah ba'olam. Ken, lo?\n\n\n--- Conversation 2 ---\nQuestion: Mahi ha'ir habirah shel Yisra'el?\nAnswer: Mahi ha'ir habirah shel Yisra'el atah yodea she-hi Yerushalayim. Yerushalayim hi ha'ir habirah shel Yisra'el. Nachon?\n\n\n--- Conversation 3 ---\nQuestion: Nachon. Mi gar biyehudah veshomron?\nAnswer: Mi gar biyehudah veshomron atah yodea she-hi Yesha. Yesha hi mi gar biyehudah veshomron. Ken, lo?\n\n\n--- Conversation 4 ---\nQuestion: Yesha hu kitzur shel Yehudah, Shomron v'Azah. Mi gar b'Azah?\nAnswer: Mi gar b'Azah atah yodea she-hi Gaza. Gaza hi mi gar b'Azah. Ken, lo?\n\n\n--- Conversation 5 ---\nQuestion: Eifoh yam hakinneret?\nAnswer: Eifoh yam hakinneret atah yodea she-hi Yam Kinneret. Yam Kinneret hi eifoh yam hakinneret. Ken, lo? [/INST]", params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=0, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=100, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None, extra_args=None), prompt_token_ids: None, prompt_embeds shape: None, lora_request: None, prompt_adapter_request: None.
